{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"c8a988cbe6","title":"和农协干部的谈话","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"2fb925434c","index":0,"year":1927,"month":1,"day":null,"articleId":"c8a988cbe6"}],"tags":[{"id":"314ad57c4d","name":"对话","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji3","name":"毛泽东全集第3卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji3.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji3":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"28b5b5206d","type":"paragraph","text":"和农协干部的谈话","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji3","articleId":"c8a988cbe6"},{"id":"9ad9ad4278","type":"paragraph","text":"（1927年1月）我从银田到韶山来，看到农民都起来了，已经缴起了一个农村大革命。过去雨神庙有很多“流民”，现在没有了，他们有的参加了农会，有的在劳动，这是一个很大的进步。[1]在部山期间，毛泽东多次召集农协干部和群众座谈。这是毛泽东和毛和轩、王淑兰等农协干部谈话的一部分。","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji3","articleId":"c8a988cbe6"}],"page":{"id":"17b3f0da60","publicationId":"maoquanji3","articleId":"c8a988cbe6","start":374,"end":374}}}},"__N_SSG":true}